article_title: Group upset over Plano Tomorrow campaign
article_text:
Plano, TX (75023)

Today

Cloudy. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. High 86F. Winds S at 15 to 25 mph..

Tonight

Thunderstorms likely this evening. Then the chance of scattered thunderstorms overnight. Low 72F. Winds S at 15 to 25 mph. Chance of rain 80%.
